quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  8,62,"Si ɓe faandike nde ɓe janfoto maa, pellet, ko Alla yonay maa. Ko Kanko woni semmbinirɗo ma e ballal Makko ngal, e (wallitagol) gomɗimɓe ɓen"
  8,63,"O woowindiri hakkunde ɓerɗe maɓɓe ɗen. Sinno a wintinonafkuna ko woni kon ka leydi fow, a woowindirtaano hakkunde ɓerɗe maɓɓe ɗen; ko woni tun ko Alla woowindiri hakkunde maɓɓe. Pellet, Kanko ko O Fooluɗo Ñeeñuɗo"
  8,64,"Ko an yo Annabiijo, Alla yonii ma [O yoniii] kadi jokkuɓe ma e gomɗimɓe ɓen"
  8,65,"Ko an yo Annabiijo, rerɗin gomɗimɓe ɓen e hare. Si no e mooɗon noogayo muññiiɓe, ɓe foolay teemeɗɗe ɗiɗo; si no e mooɗon kadi teemedere, ɓe foolay ujunere e heeferɓe ɓen; tawde ɓen ko yimɓe ɓe faamataa"
  8,66,"Jooni Alla hoynanii on,O anndii no e mooɗon lo'ere. Si no e mooɗon teemedere muññiiɓe, ɓe foolay teemeɗɗe ɗiɗo; si no e mooɗon kadi ujunere, ɓe foolay ujune ɗiɗo duŋaye Alla. Alla no wonndi e muññiiɓe ɓen"
  8,67,"Haananaa Annabiijo nde laatantoo mo dahaaɓe haa o ɗuɗɗina waraaɓe ka leydi. Hiɗon faala jawkoy aduna, Alla kan no faalanaa (on) laakara. Alla ko Fooluɗo Ñeeñuɗo"
  8,68,"Si wanaano binndoodi aditiindi immorde e Alla, lepte mawɗe memirayno on kon ko nannguɗon. [e konhoyri ndin]"
  8,69,"Ñaamee e kon ko honuɗon, ko dagiiɗum laaɓuɗum. Hulon Alla, pellet, Alla ko haforoowo hinnotooɗo=jurmotoodo"